{"article_id":"970gPXzbRvlx0TcM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump on Sunday continued to bash the Washington state judge","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"who overturned his travel ban .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"His comments come the same day","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"an appeals court rejected a demand by the Justice Department","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"to reinstate the order ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"which restricts people from seven Muslim-majority countries from entering the U.S. for least 90 days ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"halts Syrian refugees indefinitely and all refugees for 120 days .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Just can not believe","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"a judge would put our country in such peril .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"If something happens","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"blame him and court system .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"People pouring in .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Bad !","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"February 5 , 2017","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"I have instructed Homeland Security to check people","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"coming into our country VERY CAREFULLY .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The courts are making the job very difficult !","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"February 5 , 2017","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"U.S. District Court Judge James Robart ruled Friday","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"that the states","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that filed the lawsuit","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"- Washington and Minnesota -","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"had `` met their burden","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"of demonstrating","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"that they face immediate and irreparable injury","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"as a result of the signing and implementation of the executive order . ''","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Washington Attorney General Bob Ferguson sued this week","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"challenging key parts of the order as illegal and unconstitutional .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Robart granted Ferguson 's request for a temporary restraining order `` on a nationwide basis ''","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"forbidding federal employees from enforcing Trump 's order .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"The Justice Department lodged a strongly-worded response on Robart 's decision ,","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that halting the travel ban `` harms the public ''","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and `` second-guesses the President 's national security judgment . ''","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"The Department of Homeland Security announced Saturday","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"that it would not continue to implement Trump 's order ,","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"meaning business as usual at all airports .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"The State Department also said","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"it would not cancel or revoke any more visas .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Last week , up to 60,000 foreigners had theirs revoked .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"`` Those individuals with visas","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that were not physically cancelled","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"may now travel","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"if the visa is otherwise valid , ''","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"the State Department said .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Robart said","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"that Trump 's order is harmful to `` residents in areas of employment , education , business , family relations , and freedom","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"to travel . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":73,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":58,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":53,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elabo